snippet.title: Construction Simulator 2015 - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to become the biggest construction tycoon in town? 

Construction Simulator 2015 for PC and MAC OS available soon worldwide in retail and for download via Steam®. 

Pre-Order here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/289950
